trans-unit.source: Represents an expression that consists of a binary operation between two expressions.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et uttrykk som består av en binær-operasjon mellom to uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: CodeBinaryOperatorExpression can be used to represent code expressions that include a binary operator.
trans-unit.target: CodeBinaryOperatorExpression kan brukes til å representere code-uttrykk som inneholder en binær operator.

trans-unit.source: Some examples of binary operators are equality (`==`), addition (`+`), and bitwise (`|`) operators.
trans-unit.target: Noen eksempler på binære operatorer er likhet (`==`), tilføying (`+`), og bitvis (`|`) operatorer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType> enumeration represents a set of basic, commonly used binary operators that are supported in many languages.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType>opplisting som representerer et sett med grunnleggende, brukte binære operatorer som støttes i mange språk.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorExpression"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorExpression"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorExpression"></xref> class using the specified parameters.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorExpression"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av de angitte parameterne.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> on the left of the operator.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> til venstre for operatoren.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType"></xref> indicating the type of operator.
The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> on the right of the operator.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> til høyre for operatoren.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the code expression on the left of the operator.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir code-uttrykket til venstre for operatoren.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the left operand.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som angir den venstre operanden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the operator in the binary operator expression.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir operatoren i binær operator-uttrykket.

trans-unit.source: A binary operator performs an evaluation on two operands.
trans-unit.target: En binær operator utfører en evaluering på to operander.

trans-unit.source: Some examples of binary operators are equality (`==`), addition (`+`), and bitwise (`|`) operators.
trans-unit.target: Noen eksempler på binære operatorer er likhet (`==`), tilføying (`+`), og bitvis (`|`) operatorer.

trans-unit.source: Many commonly used binary operators can be found in the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Mange vanlige binære operatorer finnes i den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType>opplisting.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType"></xref> that indicates the type of operator in the expression.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeBinaryOperatorType"> </xref> som angir hvilken type operatoren.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the code expression on the right of the operator.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir code-uttrykket til høyre for operatoren.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the right operand.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som angir den høyre operanden.
